Now days it is most important priority for every person who wants extream success in life to be healthy.meaning of being healthy is doesn’t like that you never fall ill but it suggests complete and regular fitness of mind, body and heart. According to WHO definition of being healthy is:”Health is a state of physical, mental and social well-being in which disease and infirmity are absent. ” . it is also essential to be “interactive healthy” this is the most important type of being healthy because it talks about one to one or one to many public interaction in sociohealthy way.

intermittent fasting is not new concept.now days it is trending topic around the world. exactly it is the fast in which you maintain distance from food for the period of time.it can be apply twice in week, alternative day of week or it can also use in one day.
